  "id": "NLGwoXjo",
  "slug": "dis-armor-sound",
  "title": "Disable Armor Sound | 关闭盔甲穿戴音效",
  "description": "Disables all armor equip/unequip sounds for a quieter gaming experience.\n禁用所有盔甲穿戴音效，提供更安静的游戏体验。",
  "body": "# Disable Armor Sound\n\n~~Do you also hate the armor equip sound like I do?~~\n\n## Overview\n\nDisable Armor Sound is a lightweight resource pack that completely removes the default armor equip, unequip, and switch sounds. Whether you are exploring caves, fighting mobs, or just building in peace, this pack gives you a quieter and more immersive experience.\n\n## Features\n\n- **Complete silence** - Removes all armor equip/unequip/switch sounds\n- **All armor types** - Works with every armor material:\n  - Generic, Chain, Diamond, Gold, Iron, Leather, Netherite, Turtle, Elytra, Copper\n- **Wide compatibility** - Supports Minecraft 1.15 through 26.1.2+\n- **Zero impact** - Does not affect other game sounds or performance\n- **No conflicts** - Safe to use alongside other resource packs and mods\n\n## Installation\n\n1. Download the resource pack file (.zip)\n2. Open Minecraft, go to \"Options\" > \"Resource Packs\" > \"Open Resource Pack Folder\"\n3. Place the downloaded file into the folder\n4. Enable the resource pack in-game\n\n## Notes\n\n- This pack only works locally - other players need to install it themselves\n- The Warden can still hear armor equip sounds\n- Server-side players without this pack will still hear the sounds\n\n---\n\n# 禁用盔甲穿戴音效\n\n~~你是否也跟我一样讨厌盔甲穿戴音效？~~\n\n## 概述\n\nDisable Armor Sound 是一个轻量级资源包，完全移除盔甲穿戴、脱下和切换时的默认音效。无论你是在探索洞穴、战斗怪物，还是安静地建造，这个资源包都能为你提供更安静、更沉浸的游戏体验。\n\n## 功能\n\n- **完全静音** - 移除所有盔甲穿戴/脱下/切换音效\n- **全盔甲支持** - 适用于所有盔甲材质：\n  - 通用、锁甲、钻石甲、金甲、铁甲、皮革甲、下界合金甲、海龟壳、鞘翅、铜甲\n- **广泛兼容** - 支持 Minecraft 1.15 至 26.1.2+\n- **零性能影响** - 不影响其他游戏音效或性能\n- **无冲突** - 可与其他资源包和模组安全共存\n\n## 安装方法\n\n1. 下载资源包文件 (.zip)\n2. 打开 Minecraft，进入「选项」>「资源包」>「打开资源包文件夹」\n3. 将下载的文件放入文件夹\n4. 在游戏中启用该资源包\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 该资源包仅在本地端生效，其他玩家需要各自安装\n- 坚守者 (Warden) 仍会听到盔甲穿戴音效\n- 服务器中未安装此资源包的玩家仍能听到音效",
